### ============================================================
### project-service & task-service API Tests (qua Gateway :8080)
### Thay TOKEN_ADMIN / TOKEN_USER bằng JWT thực từ /api/xac-thuc/dang-nhap
### ============================================================

@GATEWAY = http://localhost:8080
@TOKEN_ADMIN = Bearer <jwt_admin_here>
@TOKEN_USER  = Bearer <jwt_user_here>

### ---- HEALTH (không cần token) ----

GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects/health

###

GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks/health

### ============================================================
### PROJECT SERVICE
### ============================================================

### [ADMIN] Tạo project
POST {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects
Authorization: {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dự án Alpha",
  "description": "Mô tả dự án Alpha",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "leadId": 1
}

###

### [ADMIN] Tạo project - thiếu name → 400
POST {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects
Authorization: {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Thiếu name",
  "leadId": 1
}

###

### [USER] Tạo project → 403 Forbidden
POST {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dự án Beta",
  "leadId": 2
}

###

### [USER] Lấy tất cả projects → 200
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}

###

### [ADMIN] Lấy tất cả projects → 200
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects
Authorization: {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}

###

### [USER] Lấy project theo ID
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects/1
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}

###

### [USER] Lấy projects theo status
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects/status/ACTIVE
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}

###

### [USER] Lấy projects theo lead
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects/lead/1
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}

###

### [ADMIN] Cập nhật project
PUT {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects/1
Authorization: {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dự án Alpha (updated)",
  "description": "Mô tả mới",
  "status": "PAUSED",
  "leadId": 1
}

###

### [USER] Cập nhật project → 403 Forbidden
PUT {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects/1
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hack",
  "leadId": 1
}

###

### [ADMIN] Xóa project
DELETE {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects/1
Authorization: {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}

###

### Không có token → 401
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/du-an/projects

### ============================================================
### TASK SERVICE
### ============================================================

### [ADMIN] Tạo task
POST {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks
Authorization: {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Thiết kế DB",
  "description": "Thiết kế schema cho module dự án",
  "status": "OPEN",
  "assigneeId": 1,
  "projectId": 1
}

###

### [ADMIN] Tạo task - thiếu title → 400
POST {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks
Authorization: {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assigneeId": 1,
  "projectId": 1
}

###

### [USER] Tạo task → 403 Forbidden
POST {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hack task",
  "assigneeId": 1,
  "projectId": 1
}

###

### [USER] Lấy tất cả tasks → 200
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}

###

### [USER] Lấy task theo ID
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks/1
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}

###

### [USER] Lấy tasks theo project
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks/project/1
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}

###

### [USER] Lấy tasks theo assignee
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks/assignee/1
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}

###

### [USER] Lấy tasks theo status
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks/status/OPEN
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}

###

### [ADMIN] Cập nhật task
PUT {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks/1
Authorization: {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Thiết kế DB (updated)",
  "description": "Cập nhật mô tả",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "assigneeId": 1,
  "projectId": 1
}

###

### [USER] Cập nhật task → 403 Forbidden
PUT {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks/1
Authorization: {{TOKEN_USER}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hack",
  "assigneeId": 1,
  "projectId": 1
}

###

### [ADMIN] Xóa task
DELETE {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks/1
Authorization: {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}

###

### Không có token → 401
GET {{GATEWAY}}/api/cong-viec/tasks
